NDI SDK COMPLIANCE INFORMATION
==============================

CUEMS Video Composer includes the NDI速 SDK libraries in compliance with the
NDI SDK License Agreement. This document provides important information about
NDI and the bundled SDK.

ABOUT NDI
---------
NDI速 (Network Device Interface) is a technology that enables video production
workflows over standard IP networks. NDI allows multiple video systems to
communicate with one another over IP, making it easy to share video sources
across a network.

NDI速 is a registered trademark of Vizrt NDI AB.

For more information about NDI, please visit:
  https://ndi.video/

NDI TOOLS
---------
This package does NOT include NDI Tools. If you need NDI Tools (such as NDI
Test Patterns, NDI Studio Monitor, etc.), please download them from:
  https://ndi.video/tools

NDI SDK LICENSE COMPLIANCE
--------------------------
This package includes NDI SDK libraries bundled in compliance with the NDI
SDK License Agreement. The libraries are installed to a private directory
(/usr/lib/cuems-videocomposer/) to avoid conflicts with other applications.

The full NDI SDK License Agreement (EULA) is available at:
  /usr/share/doc/cuems-videocomposer/NDI-COMPLIANCE/EULA

